<GeoPage title="Farriers in South Carolina | BreederHQ Marketplace" description="Find AFA-certified farriers in South Carolina: Aiken winter training, Camden steeplechase, Tryon hunter/jumper, and corrective work. Browse near you." breadcrumbs={breadcrumbs} faqs={faqs} service={service} category="Farriers" location="South Carolina" categorySlug="farriers" parentHref="/services/farriers" parentLabel="Farriers" introHeading="Farriers in South Carolina" introBody="Find farriers across South Carolina on BreederHQ Marketplace. SC is anchored by Aiken, winter training capital for Thoroughbreds, eventers, polo, and steeplechase since the 1880s. Camden's Carolina Cup, the Tryon International Equestrian Center, and a growing eventing community statewide round out one of the deepest specialist farrier markets in the Southeast." regionsHeading="Regional Farrier Markets in South Carolina" regionsIntro="Five corridors anchored by Aiken and Camden." regions={regions} specialtiesHeading="Farrier Specialties in South Carolina" specialtiesIntro="Aiken's winter training depth drives heavy specialization in advanced and therapeutic work." specialties={specialties} relatedCards={relatedCards} providerHref="/for-providers/farriers" providerLabel="Are you a farrier in South Carolina?"  listings={listings} listingsUnit="farrier" />
